      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, ¶ 1 June 1887. ¶ T. R. Wilson Esqr, ¶ Undersecretary. ¶ Sir....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.06.01</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Wilson<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">H87/5014, unit 262, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1 June 1887.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">T. R. Wilson Esqr,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Undersecretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In continuation of former correspondence<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Public service officers over the age of 60 needed an<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>order<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to the Public Service Board to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>continue in employment. M had last been extended to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>30 June 1887<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by an order of the Executive Council on 18 January 1887, and notified in T. Wilson to M, 25 January 1887 (in this edition as 87-01-25a).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have the honor to solicit, that my appointment as Governments Botanist may be continued through the next finance-year, my mental and physical strength allowing,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to carry out yet all the duties, devolving on my position. I am anxious, that while my working power lasts, it should be exercised by the consideration of the Government to the best advantage of the Department,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>created by myself.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M Wilson minuted on 7 June that the Chief Secretary had told him to respond that M's position would be extended to 31 December.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>This was confirmed in T. Wilson to M, 14 July 1887.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
